Author has written 621 stories for Sailor Moon, Fushigi Yuugi, Misc. Anime/Manga, Brady Bunch, Sorcerer Hunters, Kanon, 7th Heaven, Excel Saga, Marmalade Boy, Pokémon, Homestar Runner, Fire Emblem, Chobits, Angelic Layer, Secret Garden, Fruits Basket, Boy Meets World, Baby Sitters Club, Mario, Wish, Gatchaman, Rose of Versailles, Outsiders, Kaze to Ki no Uta, Family Guy, Alvin and the chipmunks, Simpsons, Now and Then, Avatar: Last Airbender, South Park, Azumanga Daioh, Everwood, Bridge to Terabithia, Peanuts, Card Captor Sakura, Bleach, Tiny Toon Adventures, Hey Arnold, Amazing Chan and the Chan Clan, Daria, My Little Pony, Puella Magi Madoka Magica/魔法少女まどか★マギカ, Adventure Time with Finn and Jake, and Ramona Series.

I write anime, game, TV, book and movie fic. I specialize in friendship, all three orientations of romance, humor, angst and sometimes dramatic monlogues.

My fanfic journal, in which I post random drabbles, plotbunnies, works in progress, and other fanfic-related babble:

I also write original fiction and plan to become a published writer someday. My original writings can be found here:

And just to save time: All series are property of their respective creators; they aint mine, I'm just borrowing 'em. Stories are written solely for entertainment purposes, no money is intended to be made off of them.

I have a lot of WIPs, and unfortunately writing chaptered fics is harder for me than oneshots. So updates can and will be slow. Sorry, folks!
